      "created": "2014-10-30T20:38:58.613+0000",
      "description": "Today all resources are always uploaded as long as the client wants to upload it. We may want to implement a feature where the shared cache manager can instruct the node managers not to upload under some circumstances.\n\nSome examples may be uploading a resource if it is seen more than N number of times.\n\nThis doesn't need to be included in the first version of the shared cache.",
